---

## About This Project

This is a fully hand-coded, single-file HTML website built as a design prototype and WordPress development reference for **AusFlix Productions**, based in Adelaide, South Australia.

The design is clean, modern, and cinematic — built around the AusFlix brand identity with charcoal black and signature red (#C8102E) on a warm off-white base.

---

## Pages Included

| Page | Description |
|---|---|
| Home | Hero split screen, about teaser, services accordion, stats, portfolio preview, CeyFLiX section, team carousel |
| About | Company story, timeline, stats band, full team scroll |
| Services | Full 8-service accordion list, why choose us, CTA |
| Portfolio | Filterable project grid — Drama, Film, Commercial, Podcast |
| Rent Gear | Equipment rental shop with working cart drawer |
| News | Blog/news grid with 6 article cards |
| Contact | Contact info cards and enquiry form |

---

## Features

- Fully responsive — mobile, tablet, desktop
- Custom red dot cursor with trailing ring
- Scroll-triggered reveal animations on all sections
- Animated stat counters
- Horizontal team scroll carousel with hover bio reveal
- Portfolio filter tabs — All / Tele-Drama / Film / Commercial / Podcast
- Working cart drawer — add items, remove items, running total, checkout confirmation
- Embedded YouTube video in hero and CeyFLiX sections
- Services hover accordion with red border slide animation
- All images from Unsplash — free for commercial use

---

## Tech Stack

```
HTML5
CSS3 — Custom Properties, Grid, Flexbox, Animations
Vanilla JavaScript — No frameworks, no dependencies
Fonts — Bebas Neue (display) + DM Sans (body) via Google Fonts
Images — Unsplash CDN (free commercial licence)
```

