## Brand Colours

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| Background | `#F3F2EE` | Page base warm off-white |
| Background 2 | `#ECEAE3` | Section alternate |
| Ink | `#0A0A0B` | Primary text and dark sections |
| Red | `#C8102E` | Brand accent, CTAs, highlights |
| Red Light | `#E8435A` | Hover states |
| Muted | `#9B9A98` | Secondary text |
| Rule | `#DEDAD2` | Borders and dividers |

---

## Typography

| Role | Font | Weight |
|---|---|---|
| Display / Headings | Bebas Neue | 400 |
| Body / UI | DM Sans | 300, 400, 500 |

