## WordPress Development Notes

This file serves as the full design and layout reference for the WordPress build. Each section maps directly to an Elementor or Gutenberg template block.

| Section | WordPress Equivalent |
|---|---|
| Navigation | Theme header with WooCommerce cart |
| Hero | Full-height Elementor section with video background |
| Services accordion | Elementor accordion or custom ACF repeater |
| Portfolio grid | Custom Post Type with filter using Isotope or Elementor filters |
| Shop / Rental | WooCommerce with rental plugin (WooRental or Yith Booking) |
| Team carousel | Elementor carousel or custom CPT |
| Contact form | WPForms or Contact Form 7 |
| Blog | Standard WordPress posts |

